nd the adaptive chain, i.e., VBAVBS, with respect to the average time for a slot to wait in the block and the average spatial requirement by the slots in the block, in a quantitative manner. Extensive numerical simulations are conducted on Matlab. Further, for feasibility validation purpose, an asynchronous chain algorithm will be developed and implemented by redesigning the Ethereum open source and analyzed.},
